Class RosTopicMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • ROS.RosMsgRaw
      • ROS.RosTopicMessage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RosTopicMessageCmdVel, RosTopicMessageCrackResult, RosTopicMessageLippageLog, RosTopicMessageMap, RosTopicMessageMisAlignLog, RosTopicMessagePanTiltCommand, RosTopicMessagePanTiltState, RosTopicMessagePointCloud, RosTopicMessageString

    public class RosTopicMessage
extends RosMsgRaw

    Gson object class: A general class of RosTopicMessage for all other type of Ros Topic message Json serialisation and de-serialisation

    Naming convention: For subclasses, the entire string received through the socket, use RosMessage12345 as class name For the message itself, the json string inside msg field, use Msg12345 corresponding to class name above
